{"tid":1800073,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[k-pop] After School成員Raina與Pledis約滿到期不再續約","createTime":"2019-12-27T12:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T10:09:50.000Z","uid":251328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8281d4b8854cfed873ed076aadd424383caa19ba","tid":1800073,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"bnt新聞訊<br />\n韓國人氣組合AfterSchool成員Raina（吳藝琳）將離開所屬社Pledis。27日，Pledis娛樂通過官方網站表示：&ldquo;再次告知我司與Raina的專屬合約在2019年12月27日到期。我司與Raina經過了長時間的的深入交談，經過充分討論，雙方協商決定不再續約&rdquo;。並補充道：&ldquo;希望大家多多支持和喜愛今後活躍在各領域的Raina，我司也會真心支持Raina的未來&rdquo;。另外，Raina在2009年加入組合AfterSchool，並已小分隊OrangeCaramel活動，獲得了大眾喜愛。<br />\n<br />\nPhoebe/文bntDB/圖本文出處『新聞來源／Wow!NEWS新聞網』<br />\n<a href=\"http://n.yam.com/Article/20191227357933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.yam.com%2FArticle%2F20191227357933&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=802895f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://n.yam.com/Article/20191227357933</a><br />\n<br />\n仲未解散<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾pledis<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f227f14084d4132fcafa1c5484afeb4f63825329","tid":1800073,"uid":21833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"咁After school  仲有邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3225d5db6a10debfeb2c83d1abd01dc56b8c652d","tid":1800073,"uid":124983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"原來隊野仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984d906347c4da0993d11945640e2fb32766e21f","tid":1800073,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f227f14084d4132fcafa1c5484afeb4f63825329","tid":1800073,"uid":21833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"咁Afte